OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FITV News' Nina Hossain speaks with
OL,7,Fcyber security expert Graham Cluley
OL,8,Fabout what to expect and how you can
OL,9,Fstay safe in the wake of the M&S cyber
OL,10,Fattack.
OL,12,FHigh street chain Marks and Spencer
OL,13,Fhas revealed that hackers gained
OL,14,Faccess to customers' personal details
OL,15,Fas a result of the cyber attack which
OL,16,Fhit the company around three weeks ago.
OL,18,FThe retailer says names, addresses,
OL,19,Fphone numbers and partial card
OL,20,Finformation could have been accessed
OL,21,Fas part of the breach.
