OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FWhile M&S say passwords and payment
OL,7,Fdetails were not accessed, both the
OL,8,Fshop and cyber security experts have
OL,9,Fwarned consumers they face additional
OL,10,Fsecurity risks as a result of this
OL,11,Fstolen data.
OL,13,FSo, what steps should you take to
OL,14,Fensure you remain safe if you've been
OL,15,Feffected by the data breach?
