OL,6,FWhat's been stolen?
OL,8,FOn Tuesday the retailer confirmed
OL,9,Fpersonal details had been accessed but
OL,10,Fdeclined to say how many customers
OL,11,Fwere affected as a result of this
OL,12,Fsecurity breach. These details include:
OL,14,FWhat has M&S told customers?
OL,16,FIn a statement from M&S Chief
OL,17,Fexecutive Stuart Machin, the store
OL,18,Fthanked shoppers for their continued
OL,19,Fsupport and apologised for the breach.
