OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FMr Machin stressed: "There is no
OL,7,Fevidence that the information has been
OL,8,Fshared and it does not include useable
OL,9,Fcard or payment details, or account
OL,10,Fpasswords, so there is no need for
OL,11,Fcustomers to take any action."
OL,13,FM&S confirmed partial, or masked, card
OL,14,Finformation could have been taken by
OL,15,Fhackers though they added: "For
OL,16,Fclarity and reassurance, M&S does not
OL,17,Fhold full payment card details on its
OL,18,Fsystems, which is why we use the term
OL,19,F'masked'."
