OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FJayne Wall, M&S Operations Director
OL,7,Falso wrote to customers and warned
OL,8,Fthem they, "might receive emails,
OL,9,Fcalls or texts claiming to be from M&S
OL,10,Fwhen they are not".
OL,12,FShe went on to inform customers: "We
OL,13,Fwill never contact you and ask you to
OL,14,Fprovide us with personal account
OL,15,Finformation, like usernames, and we
OL,16,Fwill never ask you to give us your
OL,17,Fpassword."
OL,19,FWhat to look out for?
