OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FCyber Security expert Graham Cluley
OL,7,Ftold ITV News it is reassuring and
OL,8,Fentirely credible that customers'
OL,9,Fpayment information had not been
OL,10,Fstolen, as the basic details on their
OL,11,Fown do not pose an immediate risk.
OL,13,FNevertheless he says customers
OL,14,Faffected by the breach have been made
OL,15,Fmore vulnerable to future individual
OL,16,Fcyber attacks as a result of this
OL,17,Fattack.
