OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,F"The immediate threat is that
OL,7,Fcriminals may exploit the information
OL,8,Fthey do have to target customers in
OL,9,Forder to to get more," Mr Cluley said.
OL,11,FTypically these could involve hackers
OL,12,Fcontacting individuals, impersonating
OL,13,FM&S, directing people to a fake
OL,14,Fwebsite, and luring them to enter
OL,15,Ftheir password in a phishing scam.
OL,17,FCustomers could also be led to believe
OL,18,FM&S was contacting them to offer
OL,19,Fcompensation for the inconvenience of
OL,20,Fthe hack, offering further details to
OL,21,Fthe cyber criminals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
