OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FMr Cluley added: "If people believe it
OL,7,Fis M&S contacting them, and the reason
OL,8,Fseems legitimate, that is consumers
OL,9,Fhave heard that M&S has been hacked,
OL,10,Fand might believe M&S wants to get in
OL,11,Ftouch to offer advice, compensation,
OL,12,For a gift card, then there are
OL,13,Fopportunities for further crimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
