OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FM&S Chief Executive Stuart Machin says
OL,7,F"there is no need for customers to
OL,8,Ftake any action" but went on to
OL,9,Fconfirm customers would be prompted to
OL,10,Fchange their passwords when they next
OL,11,Flogged on to their M&S account for
OL,12,F"extra peace of mind".
OL,14,FWarning consumers of the increased
OL,15,Frisk of further cyber attacks, M&S
OL,16,FOperations Director Jayne Wall asked
OL,17,Findividuals to be cautious as they may
OL,18,Freceive fraudulent emails from
OL,19,Fcriminals posing as the retailer.
