OL,3,CM&S cyber attack: What should
OL,4,Cconsumer's do to protect themselves?
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Graham Cluley
OL,7,Fadvised people they should always be
OL,8,Fon their guard against this and other
OL,9,Fcybercriminal attacks.
OL,11,F"That means being wary of unsolicited
OL,12,Femails and phone calls, keeping your
OL,13,Fanti-virus software up-to-date, using
OL,14,Fdifferent passwords on different
OL,15,Fwebsites, and remembering that if
OL,16,Fsomething seems too good to be true it
OL,17,Fprobably is," he said.
